Task: Wait for "Hello World!" text using Fluent Wait

Steps:
1. Navigate to: https://the-internet.herokuapp.com/dynamic_loading/1
2. Click the "Start" button.
3. Wait up to 15 seconds, polling every 2 seconds, for the "Hello World!" message to appear using Fluent Wait.
4. Verify that the text is displayed.
5. Close the browser.